HAME DIL LAGANE AATA NAHI THA..
TUMSE MILE HUM BADALNE LAGE HAI..

YU PYAAR JATANE AATA NAI THA ..
TUMSE JO MIL GYE HUM SAWARNE LAGE HAI...

HAI YAAD TUMARI DIL ME MERE PAR..
YYAD HI BANKE REHTA HAI..

JO DIYA HAI TUNE DARD MUJHE 
WO ROOJ YE MUJHSE KEHTA HAI..

KAR DE RITAAH MUJHE 
KAR DE RIYAAH....2

TERE YADO SE MUJHE KAR DE RIYAAH

